Marie Windsor https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marie_Windsor 0 Marie Windsor (born Emily Marie Bertelsen; December 11, 1919 – December 10, 2000) was an actress known as "The Queen of the Bs" because she appeared in so many B movies and film noirs.
